Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.02,0:00:05.31,Death Note OP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}Within the spreading darkness
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.35,0:00:07.98,Death Note OP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}I pledged a vow to the revolution
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.15,0:00:13.15,Death Note OP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}I can't let anybody interrupt it
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.24,0:00:18.28,Death Note OP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}I'm going to change
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.79,0:00:31.05,Death Note OP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}The future that the forbidden fruit foretells...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.26,0:00:39.51,Death Note OP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}I'm going to change the dream into reality
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.22,0:00:51.36,Death Note OP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}The ending that everybody wants.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.36,0:00:54.65,Death Note OP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}Within the spreading darkness
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.70,0:00:57.41,Death Note OP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}I pledged our vow to the revolution
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.49,0:01:02.29,Death Note OP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}I can't let anybody interrupt it
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.45,0:01:07.75,Death Note OP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}Someday I'll show you
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.75,0:01:17.05,Death Note OP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}A bright and ideal world.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.58,0:01:42.53,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You there...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.70,0:01:43.37,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.62,0:01:47.21,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm here in Japan on\Na secret investigation.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.41,0:01:50.54,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Keep this a secret\Nfrom the police...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.96,0:01:53.13,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.63,0:01:55.84,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't tell anyone that I met you.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.51,0:01:57.80,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Including my father...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.55,0:02:00.55,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I'll be off now...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.51,0:02:05.10,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's just as I thought.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.56,0:02:08.02,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I also don't want the police\Nto know
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.10,0:02:11.36,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,that I've come into contact\Nwith an FBI agent.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.77,0:02:14.69,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,If my father ever found out,\Nhe'd tell L.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.44,0:02:17.69,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Raye doesn't suspect me at all...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.11,0:02:21.12,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The police will deal with\Nwhat happened just now
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.20,0:02:23.16,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,as a regular accident.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.22,0:02:39.13,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome back.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.05,0:02:40.93,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm home.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.35,0:02:46.27,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What's the matter?\NWhy the big sigh?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.52,0:02:48.10,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Raye... What happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.81,0:02:49.81,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.02,0:02:52.27,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,By chance, I was involved in\Na bus jacking
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.94,0:02:54.48,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,A bus jacking?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.98,0:02:55.69,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.77,0:02:59.15,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,A man who robbed a bank\Ntwo days ago tried to hijack a bus.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.65,0:03:02.11,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Japan has become a scary place.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.99,0:03:06.29,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Does that mean you were\Nalso riding on that bus?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.41,0:03:07.20,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.74,0:03:11.92,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,In the end, the suspect jumped\Nout of the bus and was hit by a car.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.08,0:03:14.92,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Did he die?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.42,0:03:16.96,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. Probably...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.34,0:03:19.26,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't have any time to\Nwatch what happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.67,0:03:20.80,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Raye...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.84,0:03:21.47,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hmm?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.80,0:03:24.60,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you really think\Nthat was an accident?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.10,0:03:26.31,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.60,0:03:28.14,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, you were on that bus
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.22,0:03:30.23,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,because you were investigating\Nsomeone, weren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.43,0:03:32.73,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The criminal probably died...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.56,0:03:35.02,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Doesn't that mean...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.06,0:03:35.77,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.81,0:03:39.74,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You were indeed once\Nan excellent FBI agent.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.36,0:03:42.78,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But now you're just my fiancée.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.91,0:03:46.12,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You're no longer an agent.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.74,0:03:50.75,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't say anything about\Nthe Kira case.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.00,0:03:52.66,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't get involved or take risks.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.12,0:03:54.54,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That's what we agreed on
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.63,0:03:58.96,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,when I brought you with me here\Nso we could meet your parents.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.42,0:04:01.17,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I understand, Raye.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.38,0:04:02.63,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's just a force of habit.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.80,0:04:03.84,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.26,0:04:05.14,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.26,0:04:07.68,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry.\NDon't worry about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.22,0:04:09.64,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Once we have a family,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.72,0:04:12.85,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,you'll be so busy that\Nyou'll forget that you were an agent.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.52,0:04:16.02,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You won't have time\Nfor that habit to pop up.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.77,0:04:23.36,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But first, help me think of something\Nthat will make your father like me more.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.53,0:04:26.62,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.70,0:04:31.20,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you going to write down the\Nname of the agent now?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.41,0:04:32.16,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.45,0:04:35.00,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to write his name\Na week from today.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.37,0:04:38.92,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,If he died soon after I met him,\NI might look suspicious.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.25,0:04:41.51,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It would be better to do it
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.59,0:04:44.88,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,once they've investigated\Nmore people involved with the police.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.38,0:04:50.22,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,For now, I'll use some\Nmore prison inmates to play with L.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.97,0:04:52.60,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,L.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.10,0:04:57.94,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,There is another dying\Nmessage left by a victim.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.27,0:04:59.56,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Please send an image to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.61,0:05:03.90,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Gods of Death...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.40,0:05:09.53,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,"L, do you know? Gods of Death."
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.58,0:05:13.62,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Does he want to say\Nthat Gods of Death exist?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.04,0:05:15.29,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Watari.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.41,0:05:19.08,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Tell the police to keep\Nwatch on the prison.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.79,0:05:22.88,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,There may be someone else\Nwho will leave a message.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.59,0:05:24.72,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.18,0:05:36.60,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,There sure are a lot of humans...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.64,0:05:38.27,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you going to do it here?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.56,0:05:40.86,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll show you what I've learned
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.94,0:05:43.86,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,from all of the investigations and\Nexperiments I've done these past few days...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.11,0:05:45.11,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Experiments?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.32,0:05:46.15,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.40,0:05:52.12,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I've been testing different killing\Nmethods on the criminals in this area...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.45,0:05:59.62,Death Note Signs/Titles LG,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(537,175)\fad(834,0)}Accidental Death
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.45,0:05:59.62,Death Note Signs/Titles LG,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(312,253)\fad(834,0)}December, 26 8:30 p.m.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.45,0:05:59.62,Death Note Signs/Titles LG,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(338,328)\fad(834,0)}Dies by being hit by a car.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.91,0:05:56.16,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,First, I write the cause of death\Nand the circumstances in the Death Note...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.12,0:05:59.62,Death Note Signs/Titles LG,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(305,180)\fad(2000,0)}Sho Hanekuroda
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.20,0:05:59.54,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Then when I write a name\Nin afterwards, it becomes true.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.04,0:06:03.50,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That's something even I didn't know...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.34,0:06:05.09,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,He's here...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.26,0:06:07.26,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Right on time...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.80,0:06:13.81,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Mr. Raye Penber.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.52,0:06:17.10,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll kill you if you turn around.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.06,0:06:19.02,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I am Kira.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.02,0:06:24.94,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,If you turn around or\Nput your hand in your pocket,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.03,0:06:26.49,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I will kill you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.15,0:06:28.82,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I-It couldn't be...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.15,0:06:31.78,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But this voice...\NI've heard it somewhere...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.49,0:06:35.08,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I shall first prove to\Nyou that I am Kira.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.58,0:06:38.66,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll kill the man\Nwith the glasses...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.87,0:06:42.46,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,working at the coffee shop\Nyou are looking at.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.96,0:06:44.00,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,T-That's impossible.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.67,0:06:45.80,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't do it...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.30,0:06:52.47,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I had no choice.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.55,0:06:55.22,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought that if I didn't kill\Nat least one person,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.31,0:06:56.60,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,you wouldn't believe me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.35,0:07:01.35,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That man has been repeatedly\Naccused of sexual assault,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.40,0:07:04.23,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,but the police have never convicted\Nhim because of lack of evidence.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.90,0:07:07.36,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,He was a menace and\Ndeserved to be punished.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.11,0:07:11.03,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You may already have\Nheard from L,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.07,0:07:15.03,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,that I cannot kill someone\Nunless I know his face.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.74,0:07:20.12,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I could kill everyone you see here.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.62,0:07:22.75,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,If you have any requests,\NI'll do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.96,0:07:24.67,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,D-Don't do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.88,0:07:26.84,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I believe that you're Kira...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.46,0:07:31.09,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course, you care more about\Nyour loved ones more
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.17,0:07:35.30,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,than the people here, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.64,0:07:39.18,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Consider them hostages.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.39,0:07:41.56,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-You know about her?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.10,0:07:45.23,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.48,0:07:47.32,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I've investigated you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.73,0:07:50.74,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I shall kill everyone,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.86,0:07:54.41,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,including your family if\Nyou don't do exactly as I say.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.74,0:07:56.16,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You too, of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.66,0:07:57.78,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I-I understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.87,0:07:59.66,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you want me to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.66,0:08:01.91,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You have a computer\Nwith you, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.12,0:08:06.50,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Is there a file on the agents\Nwho've come to Japan?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.92,0:08:10.84,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,My laptop is for work. I always\Ncarry it around with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.92,0:08:12.80,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But those files aren't in it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.13,0:08:15.34,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Then take this envelope.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.97,0:08:22.93,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,First, take out the transceiver\Nand put on the earphone.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.94,0:08:25.56,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,A transceiver...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.60,0:08:27.19,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's almost like a toy...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.65,0:08:31.44,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But this won't leave\Na transmission record anywhere
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.49,0:08:34.28,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,and we can converse at\Nclose distances even underground.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.49,0:08:35.61,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,He's thought this out.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.82,0:08:39.41,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Please take the Yamanote Line.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.83,0:08:42.95,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It doesn't matter if you take\Nthe inner circle or outer circle.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.54,0:08:50.00,Death Note Signs/Titles Sm,,0000,0000,0000,,{\frz343.997\pos(357,203)}Shibuya  Shinagawa
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.12,0:08:50.21,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I shall be observing you\Nfrom a close distance.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.67,0:08:52.76,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Even when you're on the train,\Nlook forward.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.84,0:08:54.13,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Keep your eyes focused\Non one spot.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.63,0:08:57.22,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't forget, I can kill at any time.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.68,0:09:01.52,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Once you're on,\Nsit in the corner closest to the door.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.68,0:09:04.10,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,If it's taken, wait until it's free.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.70,0:09:22.45,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,First, I must ask you something.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.87,0:09:26.21,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,If your answer differs significantly\Nfrom what I expect,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.29,0:09:27.83,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I will kill your girlfriend.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.71,0:09:30.54,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Of the FBI agents who have\Ncome to Japan,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.63,0:09:33.26,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,how many are there and\Nhow are they organized?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.34,0:09:34.67,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Please answer\Ninto the transceiver.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.42,0:09:37.30,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I've heard it's f-four teams...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.38,0:09:39.34,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,a total of twelve people...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.89,0:09:42.85,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Next, take out what's in the envelope.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.31,0:09:46.18,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hmm?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.31,0:09:51.52,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What...is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.94,0:09:53.53,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Of those investigators...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.57,0:09:58.49,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Write the name of the agent\Nwho is directly in charge of you all...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.57,0:10:00.99,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,in the space at the top.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.78,0:10:03.37,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What is the meaning of this?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.58,0:10:05.16,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What is he planning?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.45,0:10:08.29,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But I have to do as he says.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.71,0:10:11.67,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,He shouldn't be able to kill\Nwith just names alone...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.92,0:10:13.92,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Next, open your laptop.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.25,0:10:17.59,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You should be receiving\Na file from your superior soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.92,0:10:22.35,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,A file of all the names and faces\Nof the FBI agents who came to Japan.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.89,0:10:24.76,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,T-This is... What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.22,0:10:28.64,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, like you just did,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.73,0:10:33.90,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,take a good look at each agent's face\Nas you write their names on the envelope.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.48,0:10:37.11,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't understand it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.19,0:10:39.70,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What is Kira trying to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.99,0:10:41.41,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What is he doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.99,0:10:47.91,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like you're finished.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.20,0:10:50.83,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Now put the transceiver and\Nenvelope with the names on it
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.92,0:10:53.67,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,back into their original envelope\Nand put them on the rack.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.75,0:10:56.55,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Now put your hands on your lap\Nand continue riding the train
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.63,0:10:58.51,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,without making a move for\Nabout thirty minutes.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.59,0:11:00.76,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,When you are sure that\Nnobody has noticed
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.84,0:11:05.10,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,that you have forgotten the envelope...\Nget off of the train.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.27,0:11:12.94,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Why? Why can't I remember\Nthat voice?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.70,0:11:23.87,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Kira...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.95,0:11:25.53,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.51,0:11:46.81,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Light... Yagami...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.01,0:11:50.27,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Farewell, Raye Penber.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.77,0:12:01.90,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Raye Penber was writing those names\Non pages taken from the Death Note.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.53,0:12:06.99,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,He unwittingly killed\Nall of his coworkers.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.29,0:12:12.83,Death Note Signs/Titles LG,,0000,0000,0000,,{\move(589,455,323,452,0,4334)}Heart attack\N\N\N\NAfter sending the files of\N\N\N\Nthe FBI investigators who came\N\N\N\Nto Japan to investigate Kira.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.46,0:12:18.88,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The rest of the agents all died of\Nheart attacks after the file was received...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.06,0:12:35.06,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,L.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.31,0:12:38.23,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,We have a call\Nfrom the FBI Director.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.52,0:12:40.82,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,L, it's me.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.07,0:12:43.19,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I've just got word\Nfrom Japan that all
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.28,0:12:45.36,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,of our agents have died.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.57,0:12:48.62,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,They all died of heart attacks.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.70,0:12:51.12,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I can only think that\NKira killed them.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.91,0:12:53.58,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,L, I'm very sorry, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.79,0:12:57.63,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The FBI will call off\Nour investigation in Japan.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.50,0:13:01.80,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's from Chief Yagami.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.26,0:13:03.21,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,L.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.34,0:13:05.88,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I have just talked with\Nthe FBI Director.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.72,0:13:08.18,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,According to him,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.26,0:13:13.39,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,you were investigating everyone\Nhere involved with the task force.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.43,0:13:15.23,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.44,0:13:16.73,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What is the meaning of this?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.23,0:13:19.94,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you mean to say that\Nyou suspect us?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.52,0:13:24.36,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I decided that it was necessary\Nto learn Kira's identity.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.78,0:13:26.07,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I cannot condone this.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.45,0:13:28.57,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I cannot believe\Nthat you would spy...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.95,0:13:30.87,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,on your comrades...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.49,0:13:34.75,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,L, how can we trust you?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.00,0:13:38.08,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Besides that, Kira killed\Nthose FBI agents, didn't he?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.63,0:13:39.88,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if they're not criminals,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.96,0:13:41.80,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,he'll kill anyone who\Nstands in his way!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.34,0:13:45.13,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Kira is really just a murderer!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.05,0:13:49.72,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,L. Another victim has\Nleft a message.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.01,0:13:56.27,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,L, do you know? Gods of Death...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.15,0:14:01.90,Death Note Signs/Titles LG,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(327,30)}L O V E  A P P L E S
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.23,0:14:01.65,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,love apples...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.98,0:14:04.23,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn you, Kira!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.07,0:14:12.53,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Raye... died...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.83,0:14:17.79,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,No, he was killed by Kira...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.42,0:14:24.88,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What? A family meeting?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.71,0:14:28.63,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if I kept it secret,\Nyou'd find out sooner or later.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.88,0:14:30.26,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll tell you now.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.34,0:14:36.18,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I am currently in charge of\Nconducting the Kira investigation.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.52,0:14:38.14,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that so...?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.18,0:14:41.02,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Dad, you sure are amazing.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.27,0:14:43.61,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That isn't what I wanted to say.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.69,0:14:53.83,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yesterday, twelve FBI agents,\Nsent to Japan to find Kira, died.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.45,0:14:56.41,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Does that mean that\Nthey were killed by Kira?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.49,0:14:57.16,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.50,0:15:02.50,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It means that Kira might kill anyone\Nwho tries to catch him...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.33,0:15:04.59,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a cold\Nand ruthless crime
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.67,0:15:06.30,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,scarier than anything\Nwe've encountered before.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.38,0:15:08.09,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Many of my officers have quit.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.17,0:15:10.34,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Dad, you should quit too!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.38,0:15:12.72,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want you to die!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.93,0:15:13.85,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.89,0:15:15.97,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You should place your life\Nbefore your job.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.35,0:15:20.18,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,No. I will not remove myself\Nfrom this case.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.39,0:15:22.23,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I will not yield to evil.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.06,0:15:24.44,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Dad...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.61,0:15:25.86,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Dear...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.61,0:15:32.03,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Dad, that's admirable.\NI'm proud of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.86,0:15:34.99,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,If something ever happens to you,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.37,0:15:38.83,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll see that\NKira gets executed.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.33,0:15:46.75,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Kira will probably kill all who\Noppose him,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.84,0:15:48.50,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,even if they're not criminals.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.42,0:15:51.93,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,We may be killed by Kira...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.88,0:15:57.22,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Think of your lives,\Nyour families, and friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.18,0:16:01.64,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,If anyone wants to be dropped\Nfrom this investigation, please resign.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.89,0:16:04.94,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,If you resign,\Nyou will not be demoted.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.06,0:16:06.15,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I promise you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.44,0:16:11.07,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I want those with the confidence\Nto stay on the case to fight Kira,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.15,0:16:14.82,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,even if going after him means\Nsacrificing everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.91,0:16:16.78,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That is all.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.70,0:16:19.70,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey...\NWhat are you going to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.04,0:16:21.04,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.96,0:16:24.62,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, right, that's him.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.08,0:16:27.13,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I remember him because\Nhe said, "Get down."
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.50,0:16:30.46,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But I don't really remember\Nthe other passengers...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.17,0:16:32.13,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that so?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.88,0:16:35.47,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I understand.\NThank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.26,0:16:42.39,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,If what I'm thinking is right,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.48,0:16:45.40,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Kira could have been\Namong those passengers...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.10,0:16:50.86,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,If that's so, I can find Kira\Nalong the path this bus takes.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.90,0:16:52.90,Death Note Signs/Titles LG,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(504,109)}Serial Murder\NSpecial\NInvestigations\NHeadquarters
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.20,0:17:03.20,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Only five people, huh?\NSix including myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.41,0:17:08.63,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,No, I should say as many as\Nfive of you are willing to risk your lives.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.50,0:17:13.46,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I trust all of you who have a\Nstrong sense of justice.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.30,0:17:16.38,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,W-Wait just a moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.18,0:17:20.10,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,L says he trusts us, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.18,0:17:22.72,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,We don't trust L.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.97,0:17:27.65,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,L, we have decided to\Nrisk our lives to catch Kira.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.52,0:17:31.77,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You should know what\Nwe mean by that.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.07,0:17:36.07,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But you never show your face\Nand just order us around...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.70,0:17:40.12,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,We cannot work with\Nsomeone like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.95,0:17:44.95,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,L.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.54,0:17:50.67,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,If you want to work with us\Nand want to catch Kira...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.42,0:17:53.96,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Would it be possible for\Nyou to come here?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.51,0:18:01.01,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Earlier, I said that I trust you all.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.15,0:18:13.65,Death Note Signs/Titles LG,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(320,346)}Please keep what is about to happen\Na secret between the eight of us.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.86,0:18:15.15,Death Note Signs/Titles LG,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(320,460)}I would like to meet the six of you\Nwhom I trust as soon as possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.03,0:18:23.91,Death Note Signs/Titles LG,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(320,306)}I would like to meet the six of you\Nwhom I trust as soon as possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.03,0:18:23.91,Death Note Signs/Titles LG,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(321,391)}Before that, I want you all to go\Noutside of the police building
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.03,0:18:23.91,Death Note Signs/Titles LG,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(320,460)}and decide once more\Nif you trust me or not.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.91,0:18:28.46,Death Note Signs/Titles LG,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(323,104)}National Police\NAgency and\NNational Public\NSafety Commission
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.70,0:18:28.41,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Why does he suddenly\Nwant to work with us?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.96,0:18:33.54,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,If he's solved numerous difficult\Ncases by himself,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.63,0:18:35.38,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,he should do the same\Nthis time, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.92,0:18:39.55,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,And judging by the way that L\Nhas been conducting the investigation,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.59,0:18:41.89,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,he'll probably send a double\Nto meet us.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.51,0:18:45.10,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,A double, huh? It's possible...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.56,0:18:47.93,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I-I trust L.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.48,0:18:52.61,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I also think we need L's help\Nin this case.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.77,0:18:54.19,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Me too...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.90,0:18:56.90,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,L said from the beginning that...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.94,0:19:00.91,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,he needed the police's help\Nin this case.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.53,0:19:03.53,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Perhaps you could\Nthink of it like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.03,0:19:06.58,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,L was waiting\Nfor this to happen.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.33,0:19:08.83,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,For what to happen?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.37,0:19:10.87,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,There were people\Nin the investigation
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.92,0:19:13.88,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,who distrusted L\Nfrom the beginning.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.63,0:19:17.21,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Then we had detectives\Ncontinue to resign
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.76,0:19:21.09,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,and our confidential information\Nwas leaked...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.13,0:19:23.59,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You can't run an investigation\Nunless you trust your partners.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.64,0:19:24.55,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,In other words,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.64,0:19:29.23,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,L was waiting for the task force\Nto get down to people he can trust
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.31,0:19:31.98,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,and who will face evil\Nwithout fear.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.52,0:19:33.44,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.06,0:19:37.98,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll resign rather than\Njoin up with L.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.15,0:19:40.44,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.61,0:19:43.82,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't trail you and\Ntry to find L.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.83,0:19:50.16,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I trust L and will try\Nto cooperate with him.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.45,0:19:51.29,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Me too...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.75,0:19:59.46,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I am currently in a room\Nat the Teito Hotel.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.76,0:20:03.05,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I shall be switching hotels from\Nnow on every few days.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.38,0:20:05.47,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,From now on, I want you to\Nthink of these rooms as...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.51,0:20:07.47,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,the de facto center of\Nthe investigation.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.85,0:20:10.93,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,If you can agree to these terms...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.98,0:20:15.61,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I want you to split into two groups,\Nwith a 30-minute interval between you,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.69,0:20:19.32,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,and come here by...\Ntwelve o'clock midnight.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.45,0:20:29.70,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Kira, we're finally at an\Neven distance from finding each other.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.58,0:20:31.75,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll do this.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.04,0:20:36.08,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll make my first appearance\Nin front of people as L.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.50,0:20:43.47,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,If you manage to find this out,\Nyou'll definitely move in.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.18,0:20:45.38,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Bring it on.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.76,0:20:50.47,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I've worked a lot during\Nthese past few days...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.39,0:20:52.48,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Think.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.77,0:20:54.73,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Was there something that I missed?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.81,0:20:57.86,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,And what should I do from here?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.02,0:21:03.40,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,L, the real battle starts now.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.91,0:21:13.45,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Please come in.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.09,0:21:28.05,Death Note ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}I dreamed a dream that no one could see,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.14,0:21:33.43,Death Note ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}I threw away everything that I didn't need
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.72,0:21:42.44,Death Note ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}I'm holding these feelings\Nthat I can't give up in my heart
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.61,0:21:48.86,Death Note ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}Even if my feet fall victim\Nto the shackles of sacrifice
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.95,0:21:53.41,Death Note ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}In between reality and my ideal
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.25,0:21:59.13,Death Note ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}I can't hold back the flooding impulses
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.21,0:22:06.59,Death Note ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}Because I have a strong desire\Nto accomplish
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.17,0:22:11.76,Death Note ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}[deceit] [fear] [vanity] [melancholy]
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.89,0:22:22.52,Death Note ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10}I'm not weak enough to believe\Nany of these negative perceptions
